鬼泣系列在全球销量超出900萬份，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ir.capcom.co.jp/english/news/html/e080220.html |title=Smokin'! Capcom's "Devil May Cry 4" Ships over 2 Million Stylish Units - Making it the fastest game in the DMC series to reach that milestone |author=Haruhiro Tsujimoto |publisher=Capcom |date=2008-02-20 |accessdate=2008-02-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080228012611/http://ir.capcom.co.jp/english/news/html/e080220.html |archivedate=2008-02-28 |deadurl=yes  }}</ref> 成为卡普空“白金大作”（游戏的销量超过100万）。<ref name="capcomplatinum">{{cite web|url=http://ir.capcom.co.jp/english/data/million.html |title=Platinum Titles |publisher=[[Capcom|Capcom]] |accessdate=2007-04-04 |date=2007-01-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070211163520/http://ir.capcom.co.jp/english/data/million.html |archivedate=2007-02-11 |deadurl=yes  }}</ref>，鬼泣4成为了运营的最热销的游戏，在2015年6月30日销量达到了300万套。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.capcom.co.jp/ir/english/business/million.html |title=Platinum Titles |publisher=[[Capcom|Capcom]] |date=2012-03-31 |accessdate=2012-07-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150208030840/http://www.capcom.co.jp/ir/english/business/million.html |archivedate=2015-02-08  }}</ref>

鬼泣系列获得整体好评。在2010年，在IGN100大PlayStation 2的游戏中鬼泣居于42位，鬼泣3居于18位。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ie.ign.com/top/ps2-games/42 |title=Top 100 PlayStation 2 Games |accessdate=2012-11-16 |author= |last= |first= |authorlink= |work= |publisher=IGN |location= |pages= |doi= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201231437/http://ie.ign.com/top/ps2-games/42 |archivedate=2014-02-01 |dead-url=yes |quote= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ie.ign.com/top/ps2-games/18 |title=Top 100 PlayStation 2 Games |accessdate=2012-11-16 |author= |last= |first= |authorlink= |work= |publisher=IGN |location= |pages= |doi= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150103190544/http://ie.ign.com/top/ps2-games/18 |archivedate=2015-01-03 |dead-url=yes |quote= }}</ref> 鬼泣被人称为一个“极限战斗”的动作类游戏分支的始祖。这种游戏专注于强大的英雄用固定格式的动作与成群的敌人战斗。<ref>{{cite book | last= Bateman | first= Chris |author2=Richard Boon | title = [[21st_Century_Game_Design|21st Century Game Design]] | publisher=Charles River Media | pages = 246–247 | date = 2005-08-29 | isbn = 978-1-58450-429-0 }}</ref> 这款游戏也被称为第一款“成功地捕捉了到了许多2D经典游戏，有着残酷无情且自由洒脱的游戏风格的游戏”。<ref name="Review1">{{cite web|last= Ahmed|first= Shahed|date= 2001-10-17|title= Gamespot Devil May Cry review|url= http://www.gamespot.com/ps2/action/devilmaycry/review.html|accessdate= 2007-03-29|publisher= [[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|archive-date= 2007-03-18|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20070318093212/http://www.gamespot.com/ps2/action/devilmaycry/review.html|dead-url= no}}</ref> 该系列已经成为衡量其他3D砍杀游戏与动作挥砍类游戏的标准，并以包括《战神》<ref>{{cite web|title= God of War|publisher= IGN|url= http://ps2.ign.com/objects/661/661321.html#previews|accessdate= 2007-04-03|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20080914173536/http://ps2.ign.com/objects/661/661321.html#previews|archive-date= 2008-09-14|dead-url= yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| date= 2005-06-16| publisher= Playstation World| title= God of War Review| url= http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=120641&site=psw&skip=yes| accessdate= 2003-04-03| archive-date= 2008-06-29| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20080629102145/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=120641&site=psw&skip=yes| dead-url= no}}</ref> 《混沌军团》<ref>{{cite web| last= Varanini| first= Giancarlo| publisher= [[GameSpot|GameSpot]]| date= 2003-08-04| title= Chaos Legion review| url= http://www.gamespot.com/ps2/action/chaoslegion/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=gssummary&tag=summary;review| accessdate= 2007-04-03| archive-date= 2007-09-30| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20070930160819/http://www.gamespot.com/ps2/action/chaoslegion/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=gssummary&tag=summary%3Breview| dead-url= no}}</ref>《多罗罗》在内的游戏进行比较。<ref>{{cite web |last=Bedigian |first=Louis |publisher=Gamezone |date=2004-09-29 |title=Blood Will Tell review |url=http://ps2.gamezone.com/gzreviews/r22035.htm |accessdate= 2007-04-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070412062309/http://ps2.gamezone.com/gzreviews/r22035.htm |archivedate=2007-04-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

但丁的自信与无畏的精神受到广泛的欢迎。他被评选为第七次GameCrush的“最坏电子游戏角色名单”中的第七名，<ref name="Gamecrush">{{cite web |author=Rocco Inzauto, Edward |url=http://gamecrush.blogspot.com/2007/02/top-10-most-badass-video-game-charaters.html |title=Top 10: Most Badass Video Game Characters |date=2007-02-25 |accessdate=2007-04-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090129042015/http://gamecrush.blogspot.com/2007/02/top-10-most-badass-video-game-charaters.html |archivedate=2009-01-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 在ScrewAttack中“十大最酷视频游戏角色”第三名。<ref name="Screwattack">{{cite web |url=http://www.thelastboss.com/post.phtml?pk=2160 |title=Top ten coolest games |accessdate=2007-04-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070809013318/http://www.thelastboss.com/post.phtml?pk=2160 |archivedate=2007-08-09 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 鬼泣系列受到欢迎致使Kaiyodo生产了一系列有关鬼泣人物的手办。<ref name="Actionfigures">{{cite web|author=Borst, Brian |url=http://www.popcultureshock.com/reviews.php?id=2243 |title=Devil May Cry Action Figures review |date=2003-06-01 |accessdate=2007-04-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060516220713/http://www.popcultureshock.com/reviews.php?id=2243 |archivedate=2006-05-16 |deadurl=yes  }}<br />{{cite web|author=Borst, Brian |url=http://www.popcultureshock.com/pcs-reviews.php?id=2243 |title=Devil May Cry Action Figures |work=Pop Culture Shock |publisher= |date=2003-06-04 |accessdate=2012-01-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120116193119/http://www.popcultureshock.com/pcs-reviews.php?id=2243 |archivedate=2012-01-16 |deadurl=yes  }}</ref>日本海洋堂株式会社为鬼泣2与鬼泣3的但丁制作的相似系列的手办。<ref name="AmazonDMC2">{{cite web|title=Amazon.com Listing for Devil May Cry 2 Action Figures |url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B000HX7YTK |accessdate=2007-04-23  }}{{dead link|date=February 2017|bot=medic}}{{cbignore|bot=medic}}</ref><ref name="AmazonDMC3">{{cite web| title = Amazon.com Listing for Devil May Cry 3 Dante Revoltech action figure| url = https://www.amazon.com/dp/B000GBN2Y4| accessdate = 2007-04-23| archive-date = 2021-07